stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> team_plan

    team_plan: team-plan\nexplore + planner agents\nCodebase discovery, task sequencing

    team_prd: team-prd\nanalyst agent\nAcceptance criteria, scope definition

    team_exec: team-exec\nexecutor + specialists\nParallel implementation

    team_verify: team-verify\nverifier + reviewers\nEvidence collection, quality gates

    team_fix: team-fix\nexecutor + build-fixer + debugger\nBounded fix loop (max attempts)

    complete: Complete\nAll verification passed

    failed: Failed\nMax fix attempts exceeded

    cancelled: Cancelled\nUser or system cancellation

    team_plan --> team_prd: Planning complete
    team_prd --> team_exec: Scope explicit
    team_exec --> team_verify: All tasks terminal
    team_verify --> complete: Verification passed
    team_verify --> team_fix: Verification failed
    team_fix --> team_exec: Fixes applied
    team_fix --> team_verify: Re-verify directly
    team_fix --> failed: Max attempts exceeded
    team_plan --> cancelled: Cancel signal
    team_exec --> cancelled: Cancel signal
    team_verify --> cancelled: Cancel signal

    complete --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    cancelled --> [*]
